org.forgerock.openam.cts.monitoring.impl.connections

Class MonitoredCTSConnectionFactory<C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.cts.monitoring.impl.connections.MonitoredCTSConnectionFactory<C>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ConnectionFactory<C>

    public class MonitoredCTSConnectionFactory<C>
extends Object
implements ConnectionFactory<C>
    A wrapper for the CTSConnectionFactory which tracks the success/failure of connection attempts requested through this factory. The tracked values are stored in a data structure which is shared by the monitoring system.
